column16: Joc Pederson singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Matt Kemp.
Juan Uribe homers (1) on a line drive to right field.    Yasmani Grandal scores.
Carl Crawford lines out to right fielder Matt Kemp.
Drew Stubbs out on a sacrifice bunt, third baseman Will Middlebrooks to second baseman Yangervis Solarte.   Rafael Ynoa to 3rd.
Rafael Ynoa doubles (1) on a line drive to left fielder Will Venable.
Drew Stubbs grounds out, third baseman Yangervis Solarte to first baseman Wil Nieves.
Charlie Blackmon triples (1) on a sharp fly ball to center fielder Wil Myers, deflected by right fielder Cory Spangenberg.   Daniel Descalso scores.
Rafael Ynoa grounds into a double play, second baseman Jedd Gyorko to first baseman Wil Nieves.   Nick Hundley out at 2nd.
Nick Hundley singles on a ground ball to center fielder Wil Myers.
Miguel Montero homers (2) on a line drive to right center field.    Starlin Castro scores.
